<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这里是哪儿？” 罗西站在一条路中间嘀咕着，“我是怎么来的？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24914</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看了看四周：“孙悟空呢？刚才他还在我面前！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24914</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30119</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西观察了周围的环境，她确认自己还在山上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30119</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37227</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是山下一片黑暗，也看不到美罗城。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>42249</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，另一条路的尽头走来两个妖怪。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>42249</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“大王抢回了他的山，现在可以放心了。” 高妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52017</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>矮妖怪点了点头：“真期待今天的宴会，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52017</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于能吃唐僧了！然后我们就能……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“长生不老！” 两个妖怪同时说，然后他们哈哈大笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63732</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>高妖怪的肚子咕噜噜叫起来：“真想马上吃……”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>矮妖怪举起手让他安静：“嘘！有人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76068</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82759</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个妖怪躲在一块巨石后面，看到一个女孩儿走在路上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82759</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她穿的衣服好奇怪。” 矮妖怪说，“不像是这里的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88358</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93200</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们吃了她吧！” 高妖怪贪婪地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93200</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98945</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等。” 矮妖怪小声说，“有人来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98945</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西也听到有人靠近的声音。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>106223</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，几个长相丑陋的男人走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>106223</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109944</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，你们好！” 罗西向他们打招呼，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109944</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112687</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“能告诉我这里是哪儿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112687</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117567</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人走向前，手里拿着大大的木棒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117567</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120979</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把钱交出来！” 他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120979</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125247</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西翻了个白眼：“你吓不到我的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125247</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人跺着脚走向罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咻！罗西的眼睛发出激光，木棒一下子燃烧起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>133889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138589</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“啊！”男人扔掉了木棒，罗西笑了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138589</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141337</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>其他人看起来很害怕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141337</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146590</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她是妖怪，快跑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146590</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看到了吗？” 矮妖怪小声对高妖怪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154813</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>高妖怪点了点头：“她的法术很厉害，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154813</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158169</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你说她是不是迅翼说的那个女神仙？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161836</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“肯定是她！” 矮妖怪回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164339</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西沿着路往前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168483</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这下麻烦了。” 她心想，“天这么黑，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168483</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172858</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我都不知道我在哪儿，要怎么回家。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172858</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176867</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，两位老人走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176867</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“孩子，你迷路了吗？” 老爷爷问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187659</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西看了他们一会儿，觉得他们看起来很友好，可以相信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187659</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>193832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>于是她说了真话：“是的，我迷路了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>193832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你看起来很累。” 老奶奶说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>202802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们在一个地主家工作，地主很善良，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>202802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你要不要跟我们一起回去？他会让你住一晚的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215917</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西跟着两位老人，来到山上的一座漂亮的大房子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老爷爷给她拿来热腾腾的食物，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222763</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>老奶奶带她去了舒适的房间。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222763</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229870</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快就睡着了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天早上，罗西和地主一起喝茶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234494</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238307</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是这里的人吗？” 地主问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238307</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240927</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240927</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247178</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地主靠近罗西：“你来自……另一个世界吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247178</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西耸了耸肩：“好像是吧。我住的地方和这里完全不一样。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>地主笑了：“你还有强大的力量。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>